"Reading CVD header (daily.cvd): OK\n"
"Downloading daily.cvd [*]\n"
"daily.cvd updated (version: 298, sigs: 1141, f-level: 2, builder: diego)\n"
"Database updated (21370 signatures) from database.clamav.net (193.1.219.100).\n"
